      <Value><![CDATA[<p>For further information, please view QMU's <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b1e7ca3e140469f96ca47eb757e6fbb}" title="Equality and Diversity">Equality and Diversity Page</a>.</p>]]></Value>
